    "These velocities can be directly executed by the wheeled robots.",
    "For quadrupeds, we use MorAL [20] to convert the robot velocity commands into target joint positions.",
    "We use the opensource model weights for ViNT and NavDP, and train MorAL from scratch using the randomly generated small-sized and large-sized quadrupeds.",
    "MorAL is used here as it is a SOTA cross-embodiment locomotion controller for quadrupeds.2) Procedure: We conducted 1000 trials for each method and robot embodiment.",
